No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF376A88FF559E211D2AB3DB" pageId="204" pageNumber="966" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF376A88FF559E211D2AB3DB" blockId="204.[167,1376,1457,2361]" pageId="204" pageNumber="966">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF376A88FF559E211C0BB3AB" bold="true" box="[169,523,2168,2201]" pageId="204" pageNumber="966">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF376A88FDE59E211C4EB3AB" box="[537,590,2168,2201]" country="Cameroon" name="North" pageId="204" pageNumber="966">Not</collectingRegion>
assessed on The IUCN Red List. Phan Luong’s Myotisis currently only known from a few specimens spread over three localities, and virtually nothing is known aboutits ecology or threats.
</paragraph>
